	a time there was an island which was inundated by floods every year. The 	inhabitants escaped death by migrating to the mainland, but they 	yearned to return to their home, and they longed to possess it once more. 	One of 	them said to his companions: "Let us make a ship and go back home." Others said: "It is impossible to make a ship, because we have 	neither the tools nor the materials
